Introduction

Song Hayoung is a South Korean singer-songwriter, dancer, and composer under ASND. She was the vice-captain, main vocalist, and main dancer of the girl group fromis_9.

Prior to her debut, Hayoung used to join hip-hop dance competitions. Hayoung appeared and competed in the show "Idol School" where she ranked 2nd place, earning a spot in the group fromis_9.

She debuted as a member of fromis_9 on January 24, 2018, with the mini album To. Heart.
